                                <div class="title">What is this website about?</div>
                                <div class="text">
                                    <p>
                                        A small but ambitious project representing a decentralized email service — InterPlanetaryEMail (IPEM).
                                        See what features it provides!
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
